java :
------ java is completely object oriented programming 
java is compiled programming lang 

Java runs with JVM (java virtual machine)

if you want to work with java programming we need to install JDK 

JDK : java development kit 

when we install JDK automatically one more software will be installed 
for us ( JRE )
JRE : java runtime environment 

