visual studio code 
--------------------  go to extentions button search for java 
install JDK : from it 
automatically java JDK and JRE will be adding for VSCODE .... 

every java file saved with .java format 

note: in java every statement ends with semicolon ; 

in java data type declaration is needed  (static typed programming)
---------------------------------------------------------------------
        int x=10 ;
        float y=10.89 ;
        String name = "srinivas";

python : no need data type  (dynamic typed)
---------------------------------------------
       x=10 
       y=10.56 
       name ="srinivas"

js: var , let  (dynamic typed)
--------------------------------
   var x=10
   var y=10.56 
   var name ="srinivas"

