data types
------------
int  : numerical data  : 2,56,78,100
float : decimals  : 10.56,56.789 ,100.00 
string : "srini" , "HI" ,"JAVA" 
char :  'A' , 's' , 'f'
boolean : true ,false 
array  :[ ]
map    : {k:v,k:v,k:v }

operators
------------
1.arthematic : +,-,*,/,%
2.logical    : && ||  != 
3.assignment : =  
4.comparison :  == 
5.inc /dec  : ++ -- 
6.relational  : < > <= >= 

Comments 
--------- comments are using for commenting the code 
comments are useful for understand flow of the code 
comments are not render output . 

java comments are two types 
1. single line comment  : // 
2. multi line comment  :  /*  ....... * /

variables
-----------
variable is a storage area 

variable name should fallow some rules 

note: variable name is custom defined name ...

1. variable name should not start with number 
2. variable name should not have space 
3. variable name should not be a java keyword or identifier 
4. variable name should not contain any special chars like 
   ! @ # $ % ^ & * - = } { } | \ / < > ! ~
5. varibale name allowed only one special char called underscore _ 


product1 
1product 
product1name 

conditions 
---------------
if : if condition checks only true blocks 
if-else  : checks true and false blocks 

else if : more true statements if any condition not sartisfy it will go for false block

switch: more true statements if any condition not sartisfy it will go for false block
nested if : if inside if statement 

